This work is a modified and ported version of codex-plugin-cc
(https://github.com/openai/codex-plugin-cc), originally published by OpenAI
for the Claude Code plugin system.

This repository ports the workflow to GitHub Copilot CLI, replaces the runtime
with a Copilot-native plugin architecture, removes the codex binary dependency,
and adds Copilot-specific flags such as --model, --effort, and --scope.

